---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import heroBg from '../assets/gallery/mandre-aerial.jpg';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Mandre | Blue Moon Apartment, Island of Pag"
  description="Discover Mandre — a small, quiet family-friendly town on the island of Pag, Croatia. Blue Flag beaches, children's playgrounds, local delicacies, and day trips."
  pageTitle="Discover Mandre"
  pageSubtitle="A hidden gem on the island of Pag, Croatia"
  label="About Mandre"
  bgClass="ph-town"
  bgImage={heroBg}
>

  <!-- ═══ THE TOWN ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mandre-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">The Town</span>
          <h2>Mandre — Small Town, Big Soul</h2>
          <p>Mandre is a small, quiet tourist town nestled in a sheltered cove on the western shore of the island of Pag. It has exactly what a perfect Adriatic escape calls for: clean sea, friendly locals, a relaxed pace, and a promenade where families gather in the evenings under the Adriatic sky.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Unlike the busier destinations on the island, Mandre has managed to remain authentic and peaceful. There's no industry, no noise, and no crowds — just the gentle rhythm of island life. For families seeking a genuine Croatian holiday, this is it.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="img-ph ph-town ar-4-3"><span class="ph-icon">📷</span><span class="ph-label">Mandre town view</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BEACHES ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--soft-sky);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mandre-grid mandre-grid--reverse">
        <div>
          <div class="img-ph ph-beach ar-4-3"><span class="ph-icon">📷</span><span class="ph-label">Mala Mandra Beach</span></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Crystal Clear Waters</span>
          <h2>🏖️ The Beaches</h2>
          <p>The entire shore of Mandre is lined with small beaches and coves, making it easy to find your perfect spot. The crown jewel is <strong>Mala Mandra beach</strong> — located right in the town centre, it has proudly held the prestigious <strong>Blue Flag</strong> since 2006, a mark of exceptionally clean water and well-maintained facilities.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Several larger pebble beaches are also within easy reach, offering more space for families to spread out. With a short boat ride, you can discover secluded coves and the breathtaking shores of the nearby uninhabited islands of Maun and Škrda.</p>
          <div class="beach-tag">🏳️ Blue Flag Beach since 2006</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FOR FAMILIES ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mandre-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Family Friendly</span>
          <h2>👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Made for Families</h2>
          <p>Mandre is one of those rare places where children and parents are equally happy. The town is compact, safe, and wonderfully walkable — kids can run freely along the promenade while parents enjoy a coffee at a seafront café.</p>
          <ul class="mandre-list">
            <li>
              <span class="mandre-list__icon">🛝</span>
              <span><strong>Two children's playgrounds</strong> — one in the town centre near Konzum, one near the larger pebble beach.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="mandre-list__icon">⚽</span>
              <span><strong>Mini football field</strong> — just a few minutes' walk from the apartment.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="mandre-list__icon">🚲</span>
              <span><strong>Bike &amp; e-scooter friendly</strong> — the promenade and surrounding roads are ideal for cycling with children.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="mandre-list__icon">🎶</span>
              <span><strong>Summer events</strong> — themed evenings with music, local food and drinks are organised almost daily on the promenade throughout summer.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="img-ph ph-promenade ar-4-3"><span class="ph-icon">📷</span><span class="ph-label">Mandre promenade</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ GETTING AROUND ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--warm-sand);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Convenience</span>
        <h2>🛒 Getting Around &amp; Daily Life</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="convenience-grid">
        <div class="convenience-item">
          <span class="convenience-icon">🏪</span>
          <h4>Right Across the Street</h4>
          <p>A small market store is conveniently located directly across from the apartment — ideal for quick grocery shopping without getting in the car.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="convenience-item">
          <span class="convenience-icon">🐟</span>
          <h4>5-Minute Walk</h4>
          <p>A second market store, fish market, and pharmacy are all within a 5-minute walk — everything for a self-catering holiday.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="convenience-item">
          <span class="convenience-icon">🚗</span>
          <h4>2-Minute Drive</h4>
          <p>A larger market store is located at the town entrance, just a short drive uphill — perfect for a bigger weekly shop.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="convenience-item">
          <span class="convenience-icon">🛒</span>
          <h4>20-Minute Drive</h4>
          <p>Full supermarkets are available in the larger nearby towns. A great excuse to explore more of the island on the way!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ LOCAL FLAVOURS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mandre-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Taste of Pag</span>
          <h2>🧀 Local Delicacies</h2>
          <p>The island of Pag is world-famous for its extraordinary culinary heritage. Two products in particular are legendary, and you absolutely must try them during your stay:</p>
          <div class="food-card">
            <div class="food-card__emoji">🧀</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Paški Sir — Pag Cheese</h4>
              <p>This hard sheep's cheese is produced from the milk of Pag sheep who graze on the island's unique salt-swept pastures, grazed by the Bura wind. The result is an extraordinarily complex, aromatic cheese — one of Europe's finest. You'll find it in local shops, restaurants, and at island producers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="food-card" style="margin-top:1rem;">
            <div class="food-card__emoji">🍖</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Paški Janjetina — Pag Lamb</h4>
              <p>Slow-roasted over an open fire, Pag lamb is melt-in-your-mouth tender, with a unique flavour imparted by the same salty island herbs the animals graze on. Available at local restaurants, it's a must-order dish for any visitor to the island.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="img-ph ph-food ar-4-3"><span class="ph-icon">📷</span><span class="ph-label">Pag cheese &amp; lamb</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ GORAN'S PICKS ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--soft-sky);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Insider Tips</span>
        <h2>🗺️ Goran's Picks</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted); max-width:560px; margin:0.75rem auto 0;">Personal recommendations from your host — updated each season.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="picks-grid">
        <div class="pick-card card">
          <div class="pick-num">01</div>
          <h4>Best Restaurant</h4>
          <p>[Placeholder — Goran's favourite local restaurant recommendation will be added here with a personal note.]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pick-card card">
          <div class="pick-num">02</div>
          <h4>Best Beach for Kids</h4>
          <p>[Placeholder — Recommendation for the best family-friendly beach, with tips on what to bring and best time to visit.]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pick-card card">
          <div class="pick-num">03</div>
          <h4>Best Pag Cheese</h4>
          <p>[Placeholder — Where to buy the best Paški sir, whether from a local producer or at the market.]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pick-card card">
          <div class="pick-num">04</div>
          <h4>Best Evening Walk</h4>
          <p>[Placeholder — The perfect evening stroll route, ideally ending at a café with a sea view.]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pick-card card">
          <div class="pick-num">05</div>
          <h4>Best Boat Trip</h4>
          <p>[Placeholder — Which boat trip operator Goran recommends for families, and which island to visit first.]</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ DAY TRIPS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mandre-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="img-ph ph-trail ar-4-3"><span class="ph-icon">📷</span><span class="ph-label">Life on Mars Trail</span></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Explore More</span>
          <h2>🧭 Day Trips &amp; Excursions</h2>
          <p>Mandre's location makes it an ideal base for exploring some of Croatia's most spectacular natural and cultural highlights.</p>
          <ul class="trip-list">
            <li>
              <strong>⛵ Islands of Silba &amp; Olib</strong>
              <span>Organised boat trips available from Mandre — car-free islands of extraordinary charm.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>🏞️ Krka National Park</strong>
              <span>Guided excursions available, ~90 min away. Spectacular waterfalls and swimming pools.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>💧 Plitvička Jezera</strong>
              <span>Croatia's most famous National Park — a breathtaking chain of turquoise lakes and waterfalls.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>🛶 Rent a Boat</strong>
              <span>Explore the uninhabited islands of Maun and Škrda at your own pace.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>🔴 Life on Mars Trail</strong>
              <span>Described as the most beautiful and unique trail in Croatia — a short drive from the apartment.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ AROUND THE ISLAND ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--soft-sky);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Beyond Mandre</span>
        <h2>🏝️ Around the Island &amp; Further</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="distances-grid">
        <div class="distance-card">
          <div class="distance-time">20 min</div>
          <h4>Pag Town</h4>
          <p>The historic capital of the island. Old town, salt pans, lace-makers, and great local restaurants.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="distance-card">
          <div class="distance-time">20 min</div>
          <h4>Zrće Beach</h4>
          <p>Croatia's most famous party beach near Novalja. A great evening option if the adults want a night out — Mandre remains peaceful.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="distance-card">
          <div class="distance-time">1 hr</div>
          <h4>Zadar</h4>
          <p>The mainland city of Zadar, reachable via the Pag Bridge. UNESCO old town, Sea Organ, Museum of Ancient Glass.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="distance-card">
          <div class="distance-time">~3.5 hrs</div>
          <h4>Zagreb</h4>
          <p>Croatia's vibrant capital — a worth-it day trip if you're staying for a week or more.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Map placeholder -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="background:var(--warm-sand);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Find Us</span>
        <h2>Mandre on the Map</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="map-placeholder">
        <div class="img-ph ph-sea" style="height:320px; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);"><span class="ph-icon">🗺️</span><span class="ph-label">Map of Mandre, Island of Pag</span></div>
        <div class="map-placeholder__actions">
          <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Mandre,+Island+of+Pag,+Croatia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Open in Google Maps →</a>
          <a href="/directions" class="btn btn-secondary">Full Directions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  .mandre-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .mandre-grid--reverse > *:first-child { order: 2; }
  .mandre-grid--reverse > *:last-child  { order: 1; }

  h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  p  { color: var(--text-muted); }

  .beach-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--ocean-blue);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Family list */
  .mandre-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .mandre-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  .mandre-list__icon {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .mandre-list strong { color: var(--ocean-blue); }

  /* Convenience */
  .convenience-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .convenience-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .convenience-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .convenience-item h4 { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-size:0.875rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--ocean-blue); margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
  .convenience-item p  { font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--text-muted); }

  /* Food cards */
  .food-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--soft-sky);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  .food-card__emoji { font-size: 2.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .food-card h4 { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-size:1rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--ocean-blue); margin-bottom:0.35rem; }
  .food-card p  { font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--text-muted); }

  /* Goran's picks */
  .picks-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .pick-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .pick-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(74,159,212,0.25);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .pick-card h4 { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--ocean-blue); margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
  .pick-card p  { font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--text-muted); font-style:italic; }

  /* Day trips */
  .trip-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .trip-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--soft-sky);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sky-blue);
  }
  .trip-list strong { font-size:0.9rem; color: var(--ocean-blue); }
  .trip-list span   { font-size:0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* Distances */
  .distances-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .distance-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
  }
  .distance-time {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .distance-card h4 { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--ocean-blue); margin-bottom:0.4rem; }
  .distance-card p  { font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--text-muted); }

  /* Map */
  .map-placeholder__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1050px) {
    .picks-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .mandre-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .mandre-grid--reverse > * { order: unset !important; }
    .convenience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .distances-grid   { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .convenience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .distances-grid   { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .picks-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 440px) {
    .picks-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
